src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c751b38dfd61cde302d5b0d2883662b91aced51","tid":1796554,"uid":256059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T17:09:23.000Z","msg":"其實咁多個月仲係講呢 d , 已經無人會理 ..出咁多篇都無用 .<br />\n今晚搵班黑警出黎, 以為市民會怪示威者..? 最終只會覺得係黑警搞事, 只怪咁多個月黎班黑警有幾仆街有眼睇.., 無論做乜都認定佢係錯, 呢樣係唔會變, 而事實上亦都都係仆街..."},{"pid":"dbbe3d00a78e40d61e239a8e68738f1edf0baeb3","tid":1796554,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T17:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01ac0c7249e959645e955f954e4963365e8da23","tid":1796554,"uid":273670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T17:36:55.000Z","msg":"就來可以好似阿爽咁有模擬器<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}